            </connector>
            <label>Recalled?</label>
        </rules>
    </decisions>
    <description>Created as part of PR1050558-2467, this flow updates the Contract Status when Employment Type is set to Leased or Locum, and it is launched from the &apos;Clinician Contract Review Approval Flow&apos;
